  "detailed_description": "As a Warlock, fund your expedition to discover rare and powerful flora through the lucrative profession of star farming. Build the ultimate space farm as you explore the galaxy and stumble onto the mystery of a dead planet. Cultivate exotic plant life, trade your harvests for credits, and customize your runs with unique powers in this roguelite adventure.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Harvest the Cosmos</h2>Venture into uncharted territories and gather an array of seeds and rare materials. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/89849ddb9d21d514c2afc134c6477e2d.poster.avif?t=1714566958\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/89849ddb9d21d514c2afc134c6477e2d.webm?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/89849ddb9d21d514c2afc134c6477e2d.mp4?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cultivate Your Bounty</h2>Onboard your trusty spaceship, transform your harvested resources into flourishing crops. Create the ultimate interstellar farm.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/e3aaef629d309714fb21db4d49018b3a.poster.avif?t=1714566958\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/e3aaef629d309714fb21db4d49018b3a.webm?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/e3aaef629d309714fb21db4d49018b3a.mp4?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warlock Life</h2>On your travels, find rare and powerful flora you can bring back to your den. These plants can then be utilised to give you powerful boons on your runs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/5de1f215c61efea055b2d039a076eb86.poster.avif?t=1714566958\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/5de1f215c61efea055b2d039a076eb86.webm?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/5de1f215c61efea055b2d039a076eb86.mp4?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Trade Among the Stars</h2>Encounter wandering traders during your galactic escapades and strike deals to sell your produce for credits. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/a73b80e1584de78c5eb79bf9be5f551e.poster.avif?t=1714566958\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/a73b80e1584de78c5eb79bf9be5f551e.webm?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/a73b80e1584de78c5eb79bf9be5f551e.mp4?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decorate Your Ship</h2>Find furniture on your expeditions and bring them back to spice up your farm.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/c4d2a995242a8c05d2322a5262e152da.poster.avif?t=1714566958\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/c4d2a995242a8c05d2322a5262e152da.webm?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/c4d2a995242a8c05d2322a5262e152da.mp4?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade Your Cosmic Expedition</h2>Spend your hard-earned credits to enhance yourself and your spaceship.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/62493a0364ce897dbbfa902f8bb163a2.poster.avif?t=1714566958\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/62493a0364ce897dbbfa902f8bb163a2.webm?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/62493a0364ce897dbbfa902f8bb163a2.mp4?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unravel the Secrets</h2>Immerse yourself in a story that unravels the mysteries of a long-dead planet. The fate of this forgotten world lies in your hands.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/b98a0192f7b4aa26daf4f3737205c06d.poster.avif?t=1714566958\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/b98a0192f7b4aa26daf4f3737205c06d.webm?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398900/extras/b98a0192f7b4aa26daf4f3737205c06d.mp4?t=1714566958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Auto-firing weapons<br></li><li>Fast runs (under 15 minutes)<br></li><li>Over 200 unique powers available to customise your runs<br></li><li>Find furniture and cuddly companions on your runs to take back to your ship<br></li><li>Expand your farm, recruit drones to aid you in the busy work, and use your profits to increase the power of your character<br></li><li>Each run takes you to many different planets, survive waves lasting 20-40 seconds and harvest as much as you can in that time</li></ul>",
